description:
Folks, I regret to say, this will be the last X Factor AU episode I am able to cap and post :-(
I am too far behind on my other work and the circumstances have become to tough to continue.
I will be stopping indefinitely from Saturday 12am Sydney Australia time.

Our top 11 contestants performed to see who will make it through the next round of the competition. But now, one has to go home.
